{"word":"ἁδρύνω","slug":"ἁδρύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁδρύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁδρός'><el>ἁδρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to make ripe, ripen</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to grow ripe, ripen</i>, of fruit or corn, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}